OL,5, Actor Idris Elba says there is no "one 
OL,6, size fits all" to tackling knife crime,
OL,7, after victims' families urged mandatory
OL,8, prison terms for carrying knives.      
OL,10,FDr Sinead O'Malley, whose daughter was 
OL,11,Fkilled in Nottingham last year, has    
OL,12,Fcalled for compulsory prison sentences.
OL,14,FElba said deterrents were crucial, but 
OL,15,Fthat some people carry knives out of   
OL,16,Ffear.                                  
OL,18,FIt comes as the government announced   
OL,19,Fplans to close "a legal loophole" to   
OL,20,Fban the sale of zombie knives.         
